OpenHKL is work in progress.
It must not be used in production without consent of the developers.
Information on the proper form of citation will follow.

The initial authors were Laurent Chapon (ILL), Eric Pellegrini (ILL)
Joachim Wuttke (FZJ) and Jonathan M. Fisher (FZJ).

The current development team is Zamaan Raza (FZJ), Christian
Trageser (FZJ), Tobias Schrader (FZJ), Andreas Ostermann (TUM)
and Ammar Nejati (FZJ)

We acknowledge the help of student intern, Janike Katter (FZJ).

ILL = Institut Laue-Langevin, Grenoble, France
FZJ = Forschungszentrum Jülich, JCNS-MLZ, Garching, Germany
TUM = Technische Universität München
